lead_paragraph: Closing-hole birdies from American Gary Woodland and South Korean KJ Choi lifted them into a share of the second-round lead at the Farmers Insurance Open outside San Diego on Friday as a host of big names missed the cut.

headline.print_headline: Woodland and Choi Lead as Big Names Miss Torrey Pines Cut
